f3aaeb05-7f80-4e14-9584-940c77217b6a.summary: PUBG: BATTLEGROUNDS is a battle royale that pits 100 players against each other. Players will land, loot, and survive in a shrinking battleground as they outplay their opponents to become the lone survivor.
